Madeleine Sologne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madeleine_Sologne 0 Madeleine Sologne (12 October 1912 – 31 March 1995) was a French actress. Sologne was born Madeleine Simone Vouillon in La Ferté-Imbault, Loir-et-Cher, France and died in Vierzon. Madeleine_Sologne ( 12_October_1912 – 31_March_1995 ) was a_French_actress .
